ChangeList.Description: Removed the **identifier** property from the [aiInteractionPlugin](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/aiInteractionPlugin?view=graph-rest-beta) resource in favor of the **identifier** property inherited from its base type.

Removed the **name** property from the [aiInteractionPlugin](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/aiInteractionPlugin?view=graph-rest-beta) resource in favor of the **name** property inherited from its base type.

Removed the **version** property from the [aiInteractionPlugin](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/aiInteractionPlugin?view=graph-rest-beta) resource in favor of the **version** property inherited from its base type.

Deprecated the **accessedResources** property of the [processConversationMetadata](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/processConversationMetadata?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. The **accessedResources** property is deprecated and stopped returning data on August 20, 2025. Going forward, use the **accessedResources_v2** property.
